message: all_tri() refactored to be more general.

Add and use typedefs for common BoundaryInfo iterator types.

Add required headers to dof_map.h  parsed_function_parameter.h

Added BoundaryInfo::get_side_and_node_maps() and removed version of BoundaryInfo::sync() that generated these maps. The previous BoundaryInfo::sync() version didn't work properly because the prepare_for_use call invalidates the data.
Use non-const iterators for erasing entries from maps.

Use non-deprecated boundary_ids() in node pack() routine.
